div.div:
Enhance documentation and functionality for futures trading
- Added comprehensive data setup guide for futures trading. - Updated README with new commands and usage examples. - Implemented resampling functionality in the CLI for multiple timeframes. - Improved contract fetching logic to allow for better handling of nearby contracts. - Introduced automated backfill and build script for streamlined data processing. - Added tests for resampling functions to ensure accuracy and reliability.
Created new branch master in chhag/ibkr-ingest-0.2.3

Add performance metrics, risk management, and trade simulation features
- Implemented performance metrics in `src/metrics/perf.py` including Sharpe, Sortino, Max Drawdown, Calmar, and Profit Factor. - Enhanced baseline training script in `src/models/baselines/train_baseline.py` to dynamically select feature columns based on non-null ratios. - Updated sequence preparation in `src/models/sequence/prepare_sequences.py` to include dynamic feature selection and improved NaN handling. - Modified LSTM training script in `src/models/sequence/train_lstm.py` to check for available sequence samples before training. - Introduced position sizing logic in `src/risk/position_sizer.py` using Kelly criterion and volatility targeting. - Added risk management functionality in `src/risk/risk_manager.py` to enforce daily loss limits and cooldown periods after losses. - Developed Monte Carlo simulation for PnL paths in `src/sim/monte_carlo.py` with a CLI entry point for user interaction. - Created a trade simulation framework in `src/sim/trade_sim.py` to manage trade execution and performance tracking. - Implemented a strategy router in `src/strategy/router.py` to decide trades based on regime parameters and market conditions. - Enhanced backtesting capabilities in `src/training/backtest.py` to utilize the new trade simulation and risk management features. - Refactored dataset preparation in `src/training/make_dataset.py` to unify feature engineering processes. - Improved walk-forward training in `src/training/train_walkforward.py` to dynamically select features and handle NaNs. - Updated configuration loading in `src/utils/config.py` to ensure UTF-8 encoding for YAML files.
